对，是的，是的

165
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:55,560
- Don't panic. - What?
-别紧张 -怎么了？

166
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:58,000
There is a man behind your curtain.
有个男人躲在窗帘后面

167
00:12:58,170 --> 00:13:01,800
- I have Mace in my purse. - No, that's okay! No, no, no.
-我皮包里有防狼喷雾 -不，没关系！不、不、不

168
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:07,000
This is my business associate Gavin being silly. Come out from behind there.
那是我同事盖文在发神经 出来吧！

169
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:11,380
Hi. Gavin. Pleased to meet you.
嗨，我叫盖文，很高兴认识你

170
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:14,820
It was my idea to stand there.
是我要站在那里的

171
00:13:14,990 --> 00:13:19,260
- Hello. I'll just go get Emma. - Okay.
-哈，我去带艾犸 -好的

172
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:23,690
So..
那么…

173
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:27,660
- why did I have to hide? - I thought it was Ross.
-为什么我要躲呢？ -我以为那是罗斯

174
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,600
I thought there was nothing going on between you.
我以为你们之间已经没有什么了

175
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,770
There isn't. There totally isn't.
是没有，完全没有

176
00:13:32,970 --> 00:13:37,540
You hear keys in the hall and you jump like a bronco coming out of the chute.
你听到钥匙转动的声音 就像野牛一样跳了起来

177
00:13:39,850 --> 00:13:42,010
