189
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:30,320
I'm sorry, Gavin.
我很抱歉，盖文

190
00:14:30,530 --> 00:14:32,160
Don't be.
别抱歉

191
00:14:32,330 --> 00:14:35,030
It's just bad timing.
只是现在不是好时机

192
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:38,460
So seriously, rodeo clown?
讲真的吗？斗牛士？

193
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:42,040
One of the best, ma'am. One of the best.
