00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:31,430
Wait. I can't sing in front of all these people.
等等，我不能在这些人面前唱

228
00:17:31,650 --> 00:17:34,010
Just pretend they're not even here. It's okay.
假装他们不在，没关系的

