-你可以看穿她的上衣吗？ -像X光一样

232
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:18,680
Bad day not to wear a bra.
今天不是不穿内衣的好日子

233
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:38,240
I'm calling about the advertising job.
我打来询问广告工作的

234
00:18:38,410 --> 00:18:41,070
Yes, I realize it would be entry level.
是的，我了解这是基层职务

235
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:45,780
Oh, so would I actually have to wear the chicken suit?
喔，所以我真的要穿小鸡装吗？

236
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:50,280
I need your help.
我需要你的帮忙

237
00:18:52,330 --> 00:18:54,420
Wow, it seems serious.
哇，看起来很严重

238
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:58,160
What seems to be the problem, Ashley Judd?
是怎么了呢？艾希莉贾德？

239
00:18:58,330 --> 00:19:02,330
I'm getting new headshots taken. So I went to get my eyebrows shaped.
我要照新的大头照 所以我去修了眉毛

240
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:05,470
I'm sorry. Moment to make fun of that, please.
很抱歉，让我笑一下吧

241
00:19:06,170 --> 00:19:10,300
I may be a sissy, but I'll still pound you into the ground.
我看起来可能娘娘腔的 但是我还是可以海扁你的

242
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:14,350
Look, it hurt so bad, I could only let her do one eyebrow, and now..
听着，好痛喔，我只能让她做一边 所以就…

243
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:17,280
they don't match!
两边不对称了！

244
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:33,690
It's like a baby caterpillar chasing its mama.
就像是毛毛虫宝宝在追妈妈一样

245
00:19:33,870 --> 00:19:37,030
You got to help me out, okay? Look, I have a magic marker.
你得要帮我，好吗？ 看，我有麦克笔

246
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:40,170
Fill in the skinny one so I don't look stupid for my pictures.
帮我把细的这边划粗 照起相来才不会很蠢

247
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:42,970
Okay, first of all, this is green.
好的，但是，首先这是绿色的

248
00:19:43,410 --> 00:19:46,210
- What the hell am I supposed to do?! - I will help you out..
-我他妈的该怎么办呢？ -我会帮你的

249
00:19:46,380 --> 00:19:51,010
but you have to promise you won't tell anyone what I'm about to tell you.
但是你要答应我 不会把我要告诉你的事说出去

250
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,810
What? What?
什么事？什么事？

251
00:19:54,150 --> 00:19:55,490
Okay.
好了

252
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:58,750
You know how most kids get their allowance from mowing the lawn..
你知道大部分的小孩都是利用除草 或是倒垃圾什么的…

253
00:19:58,930 --> 00:20:03,520
